{"tid":1650488,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[正視聽] 係時候修正不割席嘅定義","createTime":"2019-10-13T03:46:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T04:35:08.000Z","uid":171820,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2dd0278c944abc390c97f33cd5581c70150236ec","tid":1650488,"uid":171820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T03:46:04.000Z","msg":"有冇人覺得唔割席呢個term用得太濫？長此下去，左膠同小學雞只會覺得玩完冇後果，破壞抗爭士氣。<br />\n<br />\n割與不割，本來就應該在乎受牽連嘅人嘅態度:<br />\n1. 大屌係可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但亦要俾對方有道歉嘅空間<br />\n2. 冇悔意 / 屢勸不改 / 再犯就<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">視之為對家，劃清界線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>， 同時background check，免得俾佢哋累街坊。當然，佢哋亦有可能係鬼。<br />\n<br />\n有得揀我都唔想輕易講割席，但係戰爭嘉年華只會害死成個香港。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>反抗</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"a69ba6fe881d584d5f506ec7c2e12db495179d32","tid":1650488,"uid":282624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T03:46:24.000Z","msg":"［抗爭測驗］和勇一家遍地開花10秒角色鑑定<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1650465\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1650465</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3d24fda9a81a7c761f56456ff3ea48f109ed01b3","tid":1650488,"uid":297334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T03:46:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fABUi5d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfABUi5d.png&h=f4636c18&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mHTWxqe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmHTWxqe.png&h=003f1483&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3MifNYB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.l